structure.unit: ARTICLE II. BULK SALES OF PLANTS, AVOCADOS, LIMES AND MANGOES

text.section:
Sec. 8A-57. Article provisions declared supplemental.
The provisions of this article are not intended to and shall not be construed as changing, modifying, amending, repealing, superseding or conflicting with any provisions or sections of the Florida Statutes, but shall be construed as supplemental and additional thereto and not as a substitute therefor.
